'''Bandaerl''', son of [[Rykos]], blood of [[Melair]], [[High Old One]] of [[Dumathoin]], and protector of [[Melairbode]]'s essence was a [[dwarf|dwarven]] [[archlich]] of the [[Melairkyn]] clan who protected the tomb of King [[Melair I]] in the depths of [[Undermountain]], formerly home to this ancient clan.<ref name=UtLL-p28-29>
